Basic installation guide for Morphomanager Client and Server
Pre Requisites of Morphomanager
IP address assignment in Sigma Lite and other Idemia Products
Wiring diagram for Wiegand communication

title: SharePa by Idemia

creator: Idemia R&D
descriptionHtml:
Basic installation guide for Morphomanager Client and Server
Pre Requisites of Morphomanager
IP address assignment in Sigma Lite and other Idemia Products
Wiring diagram for Wiegand communication
Single door access controller setting
Morphomanager setting based on card type, bit structure, template location
a.Add device
b.Create BDP
c.User policy
d.Enrollment device selection
e.User Registration.

Note:

The prime purpose of the application is to provide step by step user Guide for product configuration.

Step-1:Go through the “Opening of Box” process Go through the Opening of Box process

Step-2: Wire connection Wire Connection Diagram of Wieg and Out . Stand-alone door controller connection.

Step-3 IP address You need to assign IP addresses in device to communicate with the Software.

IP Configuration through Pen Drive and OTG Cable (If you do not know Default IP address of the device).

IP Configuration through MBTB (If you know Default IP address of the device)

IP Configuration through Webpage (If you know Default IP address of the device).

Step-4: Software installation

To download Morpho Manager software http://www.morphomanager.net

First check system requirements before initiating the installation process.
Install Morpho Manager Server.

Install Morpho Manager Client.

Step-5: Configuration of devices with Morpho Manager
Morpho Manager Express Configuration (For Basic Configuration).
Advance Morpho Manager Configuration (You need to provide information about the configuration, which you want to configure).
IDEMIA will not be responsible for any physical damage or burn issue so please go through the document.
Please share your feedback to improve our services.

descriptionHtml:
This app is developed by IDEMIA: The global leader in Augmented Identity.

The prime purpose of the application is to provide step by step user Guide for product configuration.
Documentation: Follow this section to know more about the products and configuration, read the documents related to the product.
Configuration/Connection: Follow this section to check how to do wire connection and assign IP address in devices.

MorphoManager: Follow this section to do configuration of device using MorphoManager application.
For basic configuration follow the "MorphoManager Express Configuration" and for advance configuration go through “Advance MorphoManager Configuration"

Fault report: To report fault or to do self-diagnosis of fault in device, follow this section (Only for ID Screen Device)

Technical Support: Access to IDEMIA's Technical support Email and phone number.

Feedback: Please rate us, it will be very helpful to improve our services.

IDEMIA will not be responsible for any physical damage or burn issues, hence we recommend you to go through the documentation section on Home Page for more details.

Note: This application shall be used only with IDEMIA access control devices with MorphoManager software application.

Please share your feedback to improve our services.
